  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A board game, card game, and monster girl-raiser all in one! Build the perfect deck in this cute & casual roguelite action RPG!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having become a monster breeder, it's time for you overcome various trials and hardships with the monster girls ('monmusu') at your side, and raise them to be the greatest monster girls there ever were! Crush the competition in the arenas, and deliver their freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/46d350975af0a8f04224a199153dd8cd.avif?t=1747594161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras_big/46d350975af0a8f04224a199153dd8cd.avif?t=1747594161 width=800 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Raise cute monster girls with cards!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick and choose cards to train and strengthen your monster girls! Move forward on the map for the number at the top left of each card, and trigger events! Will you prioritize raising your monster girls? Making them fight? Or maybe you're more of a shopping fiend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/99637ae267d4fd3d90787a6670b7a8d9.poster.avif?t=1747594161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/99637ae267d4fd3d90787a6670b7a8d9.webm?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/99637ae267d4fd3d90787a6670b7a8d9.mp4?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome the competition, and aim to come out on top of all the arenas!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in thought-provoking battles, evaluating the enemies' actions with straightforward controls that only involve clicking! Fight until either side goes down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win, and now you've got your hands on some powerful cards and artifacts! Use them to take your monster girl to new heights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/5ef182c7732b4d91908067b1fb4fdfb0.poster.avif?t=1747594161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/5ef182c7732b4d91908067b1fb4fdfb0.webm?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/5ef182c7732b4d91908067b1fb4fdfb0.mp4?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And once you're done raising one monster girl...?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A delivery of Magic Stones in your name, based on your score! Unlock new cards and characters, and challenge yourself once more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise all 13 monster girl types, and become the greatest monster girl trainer there ever was!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/25318bd79082037c21246b76aa7c2b1d.poster.avif?t=1747594161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/25318bd79082037c21246b76aa7c2b1d.webm?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/25318bd79082037c21246b76aa7c2b1d.mp4?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A board game, card game, and monster girl-raiser all in one! Build the perfect deck in this cute & casual roguelite action RPG!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having become a monster breeder, it's time for you overcome various trials and hardships with the monster girls ('monmusu') at your side, and raise them to be the greatest monster girls there ever were! Crush the competition in the arenas, and deliver their freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/46d350975af0a8f04224a199153dd8cd.avif?t=1747594161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras_big/46d350975af0a8f04224a199153dd8cd.avif?t=1747594161 width=800 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Raise cute monster girls with cards!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick and choose cards to train and strengthen your monster girls! Move forward on the map for the number at the top left of each card, and trigger events! Will you prioritize raising your monster girls? Making them fight? Or maybe you're more of a shopping fiend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/99637ae267d4fd3d90787a6670b7a8d9.poster.avif?t=1747594161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/99637ae267d4fd3d90787a6670b7a8d9.webm?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/99637ae267d4fd3d90787a6670b7a8d9.mp4?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome the competition, and aim to come out on top of all the arenas!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in thought-provoking battles, evaluating the enemies' actions with straightforward controls that only involve clicking! Fight until either side goes down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win, and now you've got your hands on some powerful cards and artifacts! Use them to take your monster girl to new heights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/5ef182c7732b4d91908067b1fb4fdfb0.poster.avif?t=1747594161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/5ef182c7732b4d91908067b1fb4fdfb0.webm?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/5ef182c7732b4d91908067b1fb4fdfb0.mp4?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And once you're done raising one monster girl...?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A delivery of Magic Stones in your name, based on your score! Unlock new cards and characters, and challenge yourself once more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise all 13 monster girl types, and become the greatest monster girl trainer there ever was!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/25318bd79082037c21246b76aa7c2b1d.poster.avif?t=1747594161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/25318bd79082037c21246b76aa7c2b1d.webm?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660290/extras/25318bd79082037c21246b76aa7c2b1d.mp4?t=1747594161\" type=\"video/mp4\">